\# Biblium



Comprehensive Python library for bibliometric analysis of scientific literature.



\## Installation

```

pip install biblium

```



\## Features



\- Multi-database support: Scopus, Web of Science, OpenAlex

\- Citation analysis, network analysis, visualization

\- Group analysis with statistical associations

\- GUI application for interactive analysis

